open to speak old words and new

00:41:00.791 --> 00:41:05.898
words, too.
Poetry survives in my mouth and

00:41:05.898 --> 00:41:10.610
also in yours,
which seems like a good last

00:41:10.610 --> 00:41:14.650
sentence to end this course
with.

00:41:14.650 --> 00:41:25.000
So, thank you very much.
 

